title: My First MUI Project
text: This was my first time working with Mui and only my second time completing a React project. As you could imaging, it was fairly challenging to complete. I had a lot of trouble fixing the several errors that I made in the code but as time went on, things became much easier. I found myself falling in love with both React and Mui. I want to learn more about it and create more projects. As my portfolio grows, I know that I will become a much better programmer, not only in with React, but with all programming languages.
